content:
Generation 1 Cozy Corners is a collection of 50 Custom 3D designed isometric rooms which we call “Corners” and display the different types of “Cozy” that someone would enjoy.  We are all unique and find comfort in our own ways which means “Cozy” to you is different than Cozy to us..  These designs are NOT GENERATED and take about 8 hours straight to complete each Cozy Corner.  

These unique NFT's double as access into our community, instant utilities, and automatically added to all future "mintlists" for our larger collections that are currently already in the works. 

 Which Cozy Corner do you vibe with?  Typically PFP's and NFT's have traits to create rarity, with us it's a bit different so please understand that from the start!  Each one of these Corners takes around 8 hours to make and 1.5 hours to render making each piece about a 10 hour project no matter how we approach it.

This makes EVERY SINGLE COZY CORNER RARE due to their originality, style, and minimum stock. Each NFT doubles as access into our community, instant utilities, and added to all future mintlists for all the larger collections we are currently working on.
